                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-156-off894 t18290219-156-crimeloc897"></join>; I had had my till attempted on Monday night, and last night I saw the prisoner go out of my shop- I ran after him, and took him with this 19s. 6d. - I had seen my till all right a few minutes before; no one else could have taken it - he must have crawled into the shop on his hands and knees.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290219-156-person1457">
