            . I am a watchman. I was going by, and saw the prisoner behind the counter with his hand in the till - I did not know he was doing wrong till I heard the prosecutor call Stop thief! he ran out, jumped over the prisoner, and I took him - I found the greater part of the silver in this bag.</p>
